      "content": "Sounds good. Make sure you emphasize that while the new engine is faster, the way it handles complex, nuanced requests—like bespoke itineraries or specific cultural preferences—might feel a bit different or less \"personalized\" than what they're used to with you. Just be honest about the trade-offs so they aren't disappointed. Go ahead and send over a draft.",
